mm/damon: introduce a DAMON module for access monitoring that just works

Access monitoring requires manual controls.  Introduce a static kernel
module for making it just works.  The module can be enabled without
manual setup and provides practical but simple and intuitive access
pattern metrics, namely memory idle time percentiles and estimatd memory
bandwidth.

